text: Mansurovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Mansurovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 740 as of 2010. There are 21 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Mansurovo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
